quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  107,1,Do you see the one who denies the Judgment (to come)
  107,2,"Then, it is such a (man) who repels (and discards) the orphan (with harshness)"
  107,3,And does not encourage the feeding of the needy
  107,4,"So, (this is a) warning to the worshippers"
  107,5,Who are neglectful of their prayers
  107,6,Those who (only want) to be seen (by men)
  107,7,But refuse (to offer even) the neighborly needs